        "text_DrDDfM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>About Us<br/><br/>Our story begins with a scent…<br/><br/>My love for perfumes started at a young age – in that delicate fragrance that evokes childhood memories, in the small moments that stay with us forever, and in the instant when a scent can say what words cannot. Over the years, this passion grew into a profession, expertise, and vision – to bring everyone the fragrance that speaks to them, expresses their personality, and creates an unforgettable experience.<br/><br/>Over the past 12 years, I have gained extensive experience in the world of perfumes – from managing niche boutique stores to working closely with leading brands, high-quality ingredients, and unique methods for selecting and matching fragrances. Every store, every project, was managed with heart and dedication, paying attention to the finest details and to the needs of each customer, creating a truly personal, luxurious, and curated experience.<br/><br/>This knowledge and passion gave birth to AFRODITE DECANTS – an online store that brings you the most carefully selected and luxurious perfumes, in Cyprus, Greece, and beyond. Here, every scent is chosen with care, every brand selected with attention to detail, and every experience crafted to suit you perfectly.<br/><br/>At AFRODITE DECANTS, we believe that perfumes are much more than a fragrance – they are a way to express yourself, tell a story, create memories, and feel unique. We are committed to professional service, personalized guidance, and only the highest-quality products, so you can feel completely confident with every purchase and know that you are choosing the scent that truly suits you.<br/><br/>Our vision is to bring the extraordinary, personal world of perfumes into every home, every life, and every moment. After all, every story begins with a scent – and we are here to help you find the fragrance that will accompany your story.<br/><br/>Discover your next scent with AFRODITE DECANTS – an experience that begins in a moment and lasts a lifetime.</strong></p>",
